Rapid_City.Ashland Heights, South Dakota:
Ashland Heights is a census-designated place (CDP) and unincorporated community in Pennington County, South Dakota, United States. The population was 754 at the 2010 census.


== Geography ==
Ashland Heights is located at 44°7′39″N 103°7′57″W (44.127385, -103.132364).
